    "title": "Principal Visual Merchandiser at H&M India",
    "description": "Grow your career with H&M India! We are hiring a Visual Merchandiser for our Srinagar team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout H&M India:\nH&M India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Customer Service\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with H&M India!",
